puddle of mudd - my new favorite album if you like nickelback and theory of a deadman , you are in for a treat . this group rocks ! where nickelback 's chad punches out his lines ( most excellent ) , puddle of mudd is very melodious and has a great all-round sound going . this album is absolutely their best work to date and i am excited to hear some new tunes from this awesome band . keep 'em coming ! :